mysql与es关系对照表:
ES与MySQL对比
MySQL	               elasticsearch
database	            index
table	                type(es8后将弃用)
row	                  document
column	              field
schema	              mapping
index	                everything is indexed
sql                   query dsl
SELECT * FROM table	  GET http://
DATE table SET ……	    PUT http://
group by、avg、sum	   Aggregations
